#

Honey Balsamic Glazed Chicken

40 min
$12
330 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 4

Dietary Tags:

Gluten-FreeDairy-Free

Cuisine:

AmericanItalian

Course:

Main Dish

Tags:

EasyQuickHealthyDinner

Description

A sweet and tangy chicken dish that's ready in no time, perfect for a weeknight dinner!

Ingredients

  • chicken breasts: 4 pieces
  • honey: 1/4 cup
  • balsamic vinegar: 1/4 cup
  • garlic: 2 cloves, minced
  • olive oil: 2 tablespoons
  • salt: 1 teaspoon
  • pepper: 1/2 teaspoon
  • fresh rosemary (optional): 1 tablespoon, chopped
